proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.description

Class InputConfigurationValidated

  • java.lang.Object
    • proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.description.InputConfiguration
      • proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.description.InputConfigurationValidated

  • public class InputConfigurationValidated
extends InputConfiguration
    This class is used to build the link that specifies the request to ProteomicsDB. An InputConfigurationValidated is an unchangeable InputConfiguration that results from the method InputConfigurationChangeable.validateAll().
